      <section eId="sec_27_1011">
        <num>27-1011</num>
        <heading>Beverage container requirements</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_27_1011__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\ndecompose by photodegradation or biodegradation; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_27_1011__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>comply with minimum post-consumer recycled material content and\nhole diameter limitations as defined in rules and regulations\npromulgated by the department, and is recyclable and indicates a resin\nidentification code.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
